1251
01:12:19.662 --> 01:12:22.702
In order to get to the pathway activity, we derived

1252
01:12:22.762 --> 01:12:26.642
personalized genome-scale metabolic models or metabolic models

1253
01:12:27.442 --> 01:12:31.182
